                    <lb xml:id="uuid_a9882167-90f0-4ef2-8821-6790f0cef2f0"/><rs type="law" ref="">§
                        30 Pr.G.</rs>
                    <lb xml:id="uuid_341e8d45-386b-443e-9e8d-45386bd43ed4"/>31. März 1927</note>
            </p>
